**4. SMS Handoff Feature** (Gemini's strongest recommendation)
- When the AI is unsure or the caller is frustrated/asking for the owner, send the owner a live SMS: *"Urgent: Mrs. Jones on line — water heater emergency. Pick up now? [Transfer]"*
