## Quick Reference: The "Is This Right?" Test

When deciding whether to build, keep, cut, or defer a feature or landing-page element, ask:

1. **Does this directly help a contractor stop losing jobs?** (Core loop: answer → triage → book → notify)
2. **Does this make the system more trustworthy?** (Transcripts, overrides, SMS handoff, proof)
3. **Does this lower friction to try it?** (Demo, ROI calculator, short setup, simple integrations)
4. **Does this connect to what they already use?** (Calendar sync, Jobber, Housecall Pro)

If yes to 1–4: build / keep / elevate.
If no to all 4: cut, hide, or defer.

Invoices, estimates, analytics, dark mode, AI chatbot assistant, complex dashboard redesigns — those fail the test (for now). Audio demo, ROI calculator, Jobber integration, SMS handoff — those pass.

